{
  "id": "adv_event_2409_01_02",
  "title": "キミィー\nナンダカ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "今日の「おはテレ」のゲストは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today's guests on 'Oha-Tere' are.…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 3.0666666666999998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "大人気アイドル、TRINITYAiLEです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "the super popular idol‚ TRINITYAiLE!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.0666666667,
      "endTime": 6.63957989,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あの『ぷりてぃー★エンジェル』の舞台に出演が",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's hear from the three people who are receiving a lot of attention",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.8333329678,
      "endTime": 9.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "決まって大注目の三人に、お話を聞いてみましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "for their appearances on the stage of \"Pretty★Angel\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.1666666667,
      "endTime": 13.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "よろしくお願いします～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for joining us~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.0333336354,
      "endTime": 16.107143187600002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.3131522418
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "鈴村さんは日本を代表する名優、鈴村久美子さんの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzumura-san is the daughter of Japan's famous actress‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.3131522418,
      "endTime": 21.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "娘さんです。演技のお仕事は、今回が初めてですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kumiko Suzumura. Is this your first acting job?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.0666666667,
      "endTime": 25.6057603122,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "最近は全くですが、実はすでに生まれてすぐお母さんと\nドラマで共演してて。役者デビューは早いんですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I haven't acted much recently‚ but I actually appeared in a drama with my mother\nas soon as I was born. So‚ my debut as an actor was quick",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.8131526233,
      "endTime": 35.3646041156,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.57981929
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "小さい頃からお母さんの演技をそばで見て\n育ってきましたから、少しは演技に自信あります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I grew up watching my mother's acting from a young age‚\nso I have some confidence in my acting",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.57981929,
      "endTime": 42.9121774595,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.1131526233
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "長く愛されてる原作ですから、うちらが演じるのを\nファンのみなさんは、不安に思われるでしょうけど――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since it's a beloved original work‚\nfans may be nervous about us performing――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.1131526233,
      "endTime": 50.5708169223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.77981929
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "役者として、そして作品のいちファンとして……\n絶対いい舞台にしてみせます。観に来て損はさせません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As actors and as fans of the series…\nI promise to make it a great show. You won't regret coming",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.77981929,
      "endTime": 60.3178010863,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.5131526233
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "さすが優ね。アイドルのキャスティングに\n否定的な意見があることを分かったうえで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Indeed‚ Yu. Even though she understand that\nthere will be negative opinions about casting idols…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.5131526233,
      "endTime": 66.91052229419999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "うん。反感を持たれないように、言葉を選んで\nうまく宣伝してくれてる。頼りになるなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. She's chosen her words carefully to avoid any resentment‚\nand she's promoting it well. That's very reliable",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.1131526233,
      "endTime": 74.99648611559999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.2038784267
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それは期待出来ますね。今回の舞台、演出家は厳しい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can look forward to it. The director of this show is the famously strict",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.2038784267,
      "endTime": 79.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ことで有名なあの蟻田さんですが……大丈夫ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Arita-san… are you okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.9,
      "endTime": 85.09649069330001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……どれだけ厳しいしごきが待ってるのか\n楽しみにしとります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe… I'm looking forward to seeing\njust how strict he'll be",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.3038830043,
      "endTime": 91.3778059246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.570549671
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "（子役時代、先輩の役者さんからも相当厳しいって）\n（聞いた気が……この放送を観てたら、大変なことに……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（When I was a child actor‚ I heard that he was quite strict even with my senior actors…）\n（If he sees this show‚ it's going to be bad news…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.570549671,
      "endTime": 101.0926585119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.300050823
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "だって、うちらがしごかれればしごかれるほど……\n……みなさんに、ええ舞台をお届け出来るやん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because the more we're trained…\n…we can deliver a great performance to everyone‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.300050823,
      "endTime": 108.3576244276,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.5667174896
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-host005.m4a",
      "text": "（さっすが～！！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Indeed~!!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.5667174896,
      "endTime": 111.0029986938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.2530450345
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それでは、恒例のゲストによるジェスチャーゲームの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ it's time for our traditional guest charade game!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.2530445259,
      "endTime": 116.9940438643,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "お時間です！　ジェスチャー役は誰に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who's going to be the charade…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.9940438643,
      "endTime": 120.4699153107,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.5863865059
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい、うちがジェスチャー役をやらせてもらいます\n舞台に先駆けて、うちの演技を初公開しちゃいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ yes‚ I'll be the charade\nBefore the show starts‚ we'll be showing you my performance for the first time",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.5863865059,
      "endTime": 129.2593799752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.4530531725
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、優。ジェスチャー役を買って出てくれて\n演技が未熟な私のため……よね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ Yu. For volunteering to be the charade\nIt's for my inexperienced acting… right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.4530531725,
      "endTime": 136.46019790979997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.6530552071
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "ええんよ。うちも、これまで数えきれないくらい\n瑠依ちゃんに一杯助けてもらってきたんやから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's fine. Rui has helped me\ncountless times‚ too",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.6530552071,
      "endTime": 143.6124427956,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.8197218737
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それではゲームスタートです！　鈴村さんが演じる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ let's start the game! Tendou-san and Okuyama-san‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.8197218737,
      "endTime": 147.43333536789999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "動物を天動さんと奥山さんが当てて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "please guess the animal Suzumura-san is playing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.4333353679,
      "endTime": 151.54565475790002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 151.753047069
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "（優がジェスチャーを開始したわね……ふむふむ）\n（手と足を全部地面につけて歩いてる……四本足？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Yuu has started gesturing… hmm-hmm）\n（She's walking with all her hands and feet on the ground… four legs?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.753047069,
      "endTime": 162.3469475588,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.553047069
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
