      "text": "……瑠依ちゃんが何を言おうとしてるのか、分かるよ\n優ちゃんの演技のこと……でしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I know what Rui-chan's trying to say.\nIt's about Yu-chan's acting… right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 376.6053629977,
      "endTime": 386.90536299769997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
