      "text": "えぇ。確信が持てないから、あの場では言えなかった\n……教えて。優の演技は、上手なの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. I wasn't sure‚ so I couldn't say anything then\n…Tell me. Is Yu's acting good?",
        "id": ""
      },
